ghost-role-information-mercevil-rules = You are a member of the [color=#348099][bold]Sinder Industries[/bold][/color]. You should generally not seek to harm your fellow Mercs, or their ships.
                                             As a member of [color=#348099][bold]Sinder Industries[/bold][/color], you only take orders from your [color=#348099][bold]Captain or Mission Control[/bold][/color].
                                             You don't remember any of your previous life, and you don't remember anything you learned as a ghost.
                                             You are allowed to remember knowledge about the game in general, such as how to cook, how to use objects, etc.
                                             You are absolutely [color=red]NOT[/color] allowed to remember the name, appearance, etc. of your previous character.
